But, you know, when I was writing this book, Python for Data Analysis,

00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:52.000
my goal was to provide a primer, like a tutorial,

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:57.000
in how to solve data problems with Pandas.

00:15:57.000 --> 00:16:01.000
And so for that, I had to introduce some basics of how NumPy works,

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:06.000
so people-oriented computing, basics of Python,

00:16:06.000 --> 00:16:09.000
